      "author": "rachelatmonday (Rachel)",
      "cookedHtml": "<p>Hi <a class=\"mention\" href=\"/u/muf711\">@muf711</a>,</p>\n<p>Just heard back from the Vibe team!</p>\n<p>We unfortunately do not have validation for <code>Dropdown</code> , but you can do some validation on your side using the <code>classNames</code> props.</p>\n<p>We also created a feature request to add validation for the component <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/apple/slight_smile.png?v=12\" title=\":slight_smile:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":slight_smile:\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" /></p>\n<p>Best,<br />\nRachel</p>"
